Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We start all the lectures with a glory and excelsis deo.\NIf that makes you nervous, this is the wrong lecture to be on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Having been forewarned.\NAll right, today we're talking about reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality, as everyone knows, is a crutch.\NOur modern society pays no attention to it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't make political hay out of reality.\NOnly out of distortions of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, everyone presumes that they understand what reality is.\NAnd we asked everyone in the room, do you comprehend reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here say no?\NIf they don't comprehend reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a room full of idiots.\NWell, this lecture and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one has to do with truth.\NThis one has to do with reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is more concrete, literal.\NIt has to do with content.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth has to do with context.\NWhat one derives from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've got some interesting slides, which I hope you like, because I slaved over them.\NWe've given about 100 lectures worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,100.\NOver 50 here in Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll be approaching our 100th lecture birthday soon.\NWe'll give out free ice cream cones, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's start with the first lecture, which will, I mean, the first slide, which will remind me what we're talking about today.\NOh, oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.\NOh, we need to know how many people here are new.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are new?\NOh, there is, there is some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NBecause there's new people, we always do a brief review of the basics, just so that you have an orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we go on to the new material.\NSo, we have a few review slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And as soon as I can, oh, there she goes.\NThe map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And we remembered our pointer today.\NVery good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The map of consciousness is probably, you know, pretty well known worldwide.\NThat reality, everything that exists radiates forth an energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And that energy can be picked up.\NBy the field of consciousness itself, which is non-linear, beyond form, everywhere present, throughout all of time, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's our point of reference.\NIt constitutes the absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a lot of people have a negative idea about absolutism.\NAnd they are absolutely convinced that absolutism is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
